  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arbor Island is a short exploration game where players can take a leisurely stroll through carefully designed environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013010/extras/bf1af1dd7c6b357cea1ecd230be89982.poster.avif?t=1728664217\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013010/extras/bf1af1dd7c6b357cea1ecd230be89982.webm?t=1728664217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013010/extras/bf1af1dd7c6b357cea1ecd230be89982.mp4?t=1728664217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013010/extras/b1863ea241ca8b2a3240620413173fc0.avif?t=1728664217\" width=600 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Environments</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend a morning at the beach followed by an afternoon in the meadow or explore a zen garden before resting by a campfire. For the unwearied, there is a mushroom forest only accessible at night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Scavenger Hunts</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for hidden objects scattered across the island. Try your luck at searching for themed items thoughtfully hidden at each locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Meditation</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a break and meditate. Discover meditation spots around the island with a shuffle playlist of music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Mini Games</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for treasure with a metal detector at the beach or shoot tin cans off a fence in the meadow.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arbor Island is a short exploration game where players can take a leisurely stroll through carefully designed environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013010/extras/bf1af1dd7c6b357cea1ecd230be89982.poster.avif?t=1728664217\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013010/extras/bf1af1dd7c6b357cea1ecd230be89982.webm?t=1728664217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013010/extras/bf1af1dd7c6b357cea1ecd230be89982.mp4?t=1728664217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013010/extras/b1863ea241ca8b2a3240620413173fc0.avif?t=1728664217\" width=600 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Environments</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend a morning at the beach followed by an afternoon in the meadow or explore a zen garden before resting by a campfire. For the unwearied, there is a mushroom forest only accessible at night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Scavenger Hunts</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for hidden objects scattered across the island. Try your luck at searching for themed items thoughtfully hidden at each locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Meditation</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a break and meditate. Discover meditation spots around the island with a shuffle playlist of music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Mini Games</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for treasure with a metal detector at the beach or shoot tin cans off a fence in the meadow.</p>",
